stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> IntentRecognition: 用户输入
    IntentRecognition --> TaskSplit: 识别一个或多个意图
    TaskSplit --> SlotCheck: 为每个意图创建任务

    SlotCheck --> WaitingUser: 缺少订单号等必要槽位
    SlotCheck --> InProgress: 槽位完整

    WaitingUser --> IntentRecognition: 用户插入其他问题\n原任务继续保存
    WaitingUser --> InProgress: 用户补充缺失槽位\n恢复原任务

    InProgress --> KnowledgeSearch: 知识库任务
    InProgress --> BusinessTool: 业务工具任务
    InProgress --> HybridExecution: 混合任务

    KnowledgeSearch --> Completed
    BusinessTool --> Completed
    HybridExecution --> Completed
    InProgress --> Failed: 执行异常

    Completed --> MemoryWrite: 写入结果与客服回复
    Failed --> MemoryWrite: 记录失败状态
    MemoryWrite --> [*]
